# SME - Subject Matter Expert | Authority in an area
An SME is an authority on a specific area, practice, process, technical method or piece of equipment.
How to find them?
- from LinkedIn
- from internet, blogs and publications?

How can one become SME? and prove it?
- write a book
- publish blogposts, write about it, talk about it
- make video conferences about it

## Communication skills
- Team Building
- Teamwork
- Leadership
- Collaboration
- Written Communication
- Oral Communication
- Active Listening
- Communicating Complex Information in Digestible Amounts

